          "final": "• **Model‑agnostic LLM agent harness** – supports OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini, DeepSeek, Ollama, and more via a subprocess protocol, with built-in workspace tools (list_dir, read_file, write_file, run_shell) and permission controls.\n• **Evaluation & benchmarking** – JSONL-based task runner that measures success rate, tool accuracy, latency, token usage, cost, and failure categories; supports multi‑provider comparisons and leaderboards.\n• **Trace, replay & determinism** – saves complete JSON transcripts, renders Markdown traces with Mermaid flowcharts, replays runs without a model, and measures consistency across repeated tasks.\n• **Interactive HTML dashboard** – visualizes benchmark health, provider comparisons, evaluation tables with filtering/sorting, charts, transcript inspection, and local RAG search.\n• **Local lexical RAG** – indexes project documents and answers questions with cited source chunks, designed to be extended with embedding‑backed semantic search.",
